t Letter (1911 film)|The Scarlet Letter]]'' * ''[[The Smuggler (1911 film)|The Smuggler]]'' * ''[[Sweet Memories]]'' * ''[[Swords and Hearts]]'', directed by [[D. W. Griffith]] * ''[[A Tale of Two Cities (1911 film)|A Tale of Two Cities]]'' * ''[[That's Happiness]]'' * ''[[What Shall We Do with Our Old?]]'' * ''Windsor McCay And His Animated Pictures'' * ''[[Won by Wireless]]'' {{div col end}}
